FASA Star Trek

New FASA Carrier Models

Captain Mojo has released new carrier models for Star Trek games

Captain Mojo has released new carrier models for Star Trek games.

This is a follow-up on my last kit, which covered TOS era Federation carriers. In this kit we move forward a few decades to The Motion Picture era.

As noted in the previous kit, there’s zero on-screen canonical evidence of fighters or carriers pre-Dominion war (aside from the quasi-canonical Star Fleet Battles designs, which I do not cover). In this kit, I’ve pulled from Fanon designs found at the web site shipschematics.net, as well as ships of my own devising.
